{
  "stem": "24242.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He doesn't tell the whole story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So my brother Zisl told him, if you think that you a hero, try to take it back, and you'll find out what kind of a hero I am.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm translating you word by word.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You wanted to know what kind of a brothers I had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When my brother was talking to him, he walked around with a short machine gun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It had 71 bullets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can spray that within a second, and you can make it that each bullet will come out one by one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if you know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He held his finger on the trigger against this commander.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In the back of my brother was Viktor Sadutant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was an Uzbek.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "To him, to kill a person was easier than for you to clean the-- to take a hair off the table.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Curban.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had an automatic pistol right in the back of my brother's head, which my brother did not know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] By a lot came-- by pure luck, showed up, Platon, which he was the highest commander of the whole Russian partisan's estate of White Russia.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He knew both.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He knew my brother, and he knew the Russian commander.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that Platon went, the commander, Sadutant, had his pistol behind my brother's neck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He knocked his hand down, the chief of all the partisans, the state of White Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's why my brother find out that he had a gun behind his neck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he straighten it out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Obvious, it should not happen again, but there were Jewish-- there-- there were Russian partisans.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
